snippet.title: Schedule I Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Schedule I is now available on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3164500/Schedule_I/

Jump into the streets of Hyland Point and take the first steps from small-time dope pusher to kingpin. Manufacture and distribute a range of drugs to reach the peak of the underworld.

https://www.scheduleonegame.com/

Download the full-quality trailer here: https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/1a9Z2QyCHertBCtJS4vmMcSRdpXAvRsYW

Created by TVGS. Trailer music composed by Joel Ibbott.
